       >>SOURCE FORMAT FREE
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. sum.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 n       BINARY-LONG.
01 i       BINARY-LONG.
01 sum     BINARY-LONG VALUE 0.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
DISPLAY "Enter a positive integer"
ACCEPT n
PERFORM VARYING i FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL i > n
       ADD i TO sum
END-PERFORM
DISPLAY "The sum is " sum.

STOP RUN.
